kpi.name: M8011C83

kpi_info.title: Cell DL Composite Available Capacity in the range 20 < DL CAC <= 40
kpi_info.use: This counter is a part of the histogram "Cell DL Composite Available Capacity (DL CAC)" and provides the number of events when the measured downlink CAC of the cell was in the range 20 < DL CAC <= 40.

kpi.kpi_alias: Cell DL Composite Available Capacity in the range 20 < DL CAC <= 40
